eness and flexibility, are compatible with those limits.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aPhilosophy. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertStanford University Press Archive eBook-Package Pre-2000z97831107042110 cprintz978080471179140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476668540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804766685423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804766685/original  a978-3-11-070421-1  Stanford University Press Archive eBook-Package Pre-2000b2000  aGBV-deGruyter-alles